snippet.title: On My Own: Wilderness Survival Adventure
snippet.description:
Craft your own tools and manage your resources in this tranquil survival adventure. Charming naturescapes and original music frame your quest to conquer the mountain as you endeavor to make the most of your “one wild and precious life.”

⛰Play ON MY OWN 🌲
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/351730/On_My_Own/
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/on-my-own/id952029231
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beachinteractive.omo&hl=en_US
